WEBVTT

00:06.653 --> 00:09.178
<i>In New York City's
war on crime,</i>

00:09.256 --> 00:11.315
<i>the worst criminal offenders
are pursued</i>

00:11.391 --> 00:14.121
<i>by the detectives
of the Major Case Squad.</i>

00:14.194 --> 00:16.024
<i>These are their stories.</i>

00:18.000 --> 00:24.074
